root: ^Willow! You surprised me! What do you need?
^Oh? Is it about the training? I thought we weren't doing it today?
^Well yes... but no... that's not it!
^Oh. It must be pretty important! That's good because I wanted to talk to you too.
^Well I'll go first... I heard ya... calling me cute last time...
^Oh! uhmm! You heard that! I didn't know...
^Well! no worries! I wanted to say.... I think you're cute too...
^I like being with you.... a lot... like a lot... a lot..
^Really? That's great because I do too! I wanted to ask you...
^Do you want to be with me!
^I was so stressed to ask you out! I'm so happy!
^Perfect! I want to go everywhere with you! Can... I... can I call you dear?
